      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Dissolve your<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> in a heatproof bowl with 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>couscous</strong>, stir, cover and set aside</p>",
