    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add your <strong>salmon fillet[s] </strong>to the pan, skin-side down, with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Sprinkle your <strong>ras el hanout</strong> over the fish and cook for 9-10 min, turning once halfway, or until cooked through – this is your <strong>spiced salmon</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it's opaque and flakes easily</p>",
